   <talk_paragraph index="n098_warrior_master_lodrigo-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n098_warrior_master_lodrigo-1-a" mid="20" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Yes, I arrive here from Calderock Village.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Warrior Rodrigo$<BR>Hmm, an unfamiliar face. Are you new?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n098_warrior_master_lodrigo-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n098_warrior_master_lodrigo-1-b" mid="22" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Speaking a little weirdly, ignore it.)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Warrior Rodrigo$<BR>Speaking of that, I heard the airship that crashed near Calderock has finished its repairs. <FONT color=#a82424>Horses without legs can travel thousand miles</FONT>, and airship without legs can fly even further!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n098_warrior_master_lodrigo-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n098_warrior_master_lodrigo-1-c" mid="24" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Warrior Rodrigo$<BR>Alright, newcomer. Do your best.<BR>That way, you will be as successful as I am. I also experienced a lot of hardship when I first came here from <FONT color=#a94407>Lotus Marsh</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n098_warrior_master_lodrigo-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n098_warrior_master_lodrigo-1-d" mid="26" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(What is he saying? Whatever.)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Warrior Rodrigo$<BR>Have you heard of the saying that <FONT color=#a82424>falling down in Saint Haven can break your nose</FONT> ? It can be quite a jarring experience when you first start in Saint Haven. The lingo here is difficult to pick up, so it is hard to get some work at first.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n098_warrior_master_lodrigo-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n098_warrior_master_lodrigo-1-e" mid="28" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>You have put in your all.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Warrior Rodrigo$<BR>I even had to lie that I come from another kingdom in order to get grants. <FONT color=#7e12d2>(Rodrigo seems to be in a state of deep misery, and even wiped his tears.)</FONT><BR>Ahem, I am a busy man.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n098_warrior_master_lodrigo-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n098_warrior_master_lodrigo-1-f" mid="30" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Even if the sky collapsed, there will be somebody else to hold it up. (Decided to point it out.)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Warrior Rodrigo$<BR>But I overcame it all!<BR>Isn't there a phrase that <FONT color=#a82424>Even if the sky collapsed, the earthworms will still live</FONT>? Only the quick-witted can survive in this world.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n098_warrior_master_lodrigo-1-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n098_warrior_master_lodrigo-1-g" mid="32" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Ehh?！</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="31"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Warrior Rodrigo$<BR>Don't dwell on details!<BR>Open your mind and embrace the horizons!<BR>But, you!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n098_warrior_master_lodrigo-1-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n098_warrior_master_lodrigo-1-h" mid="34" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Yes, I have not seen you before.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="33"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Warrior Rodrigo$<BR>Have I seen you somewhere before?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n098_warrior_master_lodrigo-1-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n098_warrior_master_lodrigo-2" mid="36" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Do you know my father?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="35"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Warrior Rodrigo$<BR>You, look just like Sir <FONT color=#a94407>Rambert</FONT>.<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Rambert that is my father's name?)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n098_warrior_master_lodrigo-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n098_warrior_master_lodrigo-2-a" mid="38" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>It is true...</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="37"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Warrior Rodrigo$<BR>Gwahahaha! You know how to joke. I knew everything about him, all except that he had a son like you.<BR>Already lying at such a young age.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n098_warrior_master_lodrigo-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n098_warrior_master_lodrigo-2-b" mid="40" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="39"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Warrior Rodrigo$<BR>He was my idol, I learned everything about him.<BR>I even fought beside him in a battle before. It was during the <FONT color=#a82424>Great Dragon War</FONT> where he drove back <FONT color=#a82424>hundreds of monsters</FONT> all by himself.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n098_warrior_master_lodrigo-2-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n098_warrior_master_lodrigo-2-c" mid="42" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Oh, so he was Baldur's disciple?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="41"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Warrior Rodrigo$<BR>Since then, everyone started calling him the <FONT color=#a94407>Blue Wolf on the Desert</FONT>. However, <FONT color=#a94407>Baldur</FONT> who repelled <FONT color=#a82424>thousands</FONT> of monsters was a lot stronger. <BR>Is there no disciple who can surpass his master?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n098_warrior_master_lodrigo-2-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n098_warrior_master_lodrigo-2-d" mid="44" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Didn't I say that he is my father?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="43"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Warrior Rodrigo$<BR>Sir <FONT color=#a94407>Baldur's </FONT><FONT color=#a82424>last disciple</FONT>.<BR>But why did you ask this kind of question?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n098_warrior_master_lodrigo-2-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n098_warrior_master_lodrigo-2-e" mid="46" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>So where is he now?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="45"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Warrior Rodrigo$<BR>Did you eat something wrong?<BR>If you are hurting some where, you can get some medicine from the witch Stella.<BR>But don't tell her I called her a witch!!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n098_warrior_master_lodrigo-2-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n098_warrior_master_lodrigo-2-f" mid="48" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Speaking to him further probably won't be of any help to me)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="47"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Warrior Rodrigo$<BR>Yeah, he was last seen at <FONT color=#a94407>Lotus Marsh</FONT>. Nobody knows where he went from there. Even if I know, I won't tell a rookie like you.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n098_warrior_master_lodrigo-2-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n098_warrior_master_lodrigo-3" mid="50" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#086171>(Receive Reward)</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
